title: BigFish Games - Herods Lost Tomb - New Hidden Object [h33t][Wend
description:
Herod&#039;s Lost Tomb features five mini-games and 16 locations based on 
scenery taken from National Geographic&#039;s world famous photo library. 
The game will also feature footage and highlights from the show, and 
voice-overs. A reusable hint system will ensure that players never yet 
stuck.
I loved music and graphics of this game,
you can set volume from options menu,
precracked, just install and play!
